  <brief_title>Effect of Saxagliptin on Pre-Diabetes Mellitus and Obesity</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effect of Saxagliptin on Body Fat , Glucose and Beta Cell Function in Patients With Newly Diagnosed Pre-Diabetes Mellitus and Obesity</official_title>
